Class AbstractVariable

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.model.AbstractVariable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Variable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractNumericalVariable, BooleanVariable, MultiSelectVariable, ProcedureVariable

    @Entity
public abstract class AbstractVariable
extends java.lang.Object
implements Variable
    Implements base properties for Variable. Unlike the latter, this class presents a mutable interface.
